    "name": "TenantTrails API – Lab 4",
    "_postman_id": "tt-api-collection-v3",
    "description": "Full collection for Lab 4.\n\nNOTE: Auth is now cookie-based.\nIn Postman: Settings → Cookies → ensure cookies are enabled.\nThe login/signup requests set an httpOnly cookie automatically.\nAll subsequent requests use that cookie — no manual token copy needed.\n\nRun order for full flow:\n1. Signup or Login\n2. GET /me\n3. GET /apartments\n4. GET /apartments/:slug\n5. POST review\n6. PUT review\n7. POST comment\n8. DELETE comment\n9. DELETE review\n10. GET /profile\n11. PUT /profile\n12. DELETE /profile (account)\n13. Logout",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
